        "text_VdJYYkELN6DmlQ5a": "<p>You’re fully covered for 365 full days against any internal or external defects, no questions asked.</p>",
        "text_5KaWEgatKjHDHcgA": "<p><strong>NO B.S. LIFETIME WARRANTY:</strong></p>",
        "text_H5Y30nQIWOzVq258": "<p><strong>BREAK IT. WE&apos;LL REPLACE IT.</strong></p>",
        "text_YWg8AScJ8ZjIlms0": "<p>If your watch ever fails, we&apos;ll send you a new one FOR FREE. No questions asked.</p>",
